  "title": "Clinic Assistant / Clinic Coordinator #75413",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Healthcare/ Medical (Aesthetic Clinic)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Clinic Assistant / Clinic Coordinator</strong></li><li>Working Location: Orchard</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon – Fri, 8.30am – 5pm; Sat 8.30am – 3pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and assist walk-in patients and visitors</li><li>Patient registration and appointment scheduling</li><li>Respond to general phone and email enquiries</li><li>Assist doctor with aesthetic procedures (e.g., laser, botox, fillers) and non-invasive treatments (e.g., RF, HIFU, facials)</li><li>Handle billing processes and manage inventory</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a CIDESCO diploma or equivalent</li><li>Minimum 1 year of relevant experience in the healthcare/clinic setting</li><li>Computer-literate</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75413 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
